      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* subscription */}
  <h2 id='subscription'>订阅</h2>
  <p>当前订阅的服务如下（包含AFF链接）：</p>
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='订阅服务'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Aliyun',
        description: 'Domain,DNS,Servers | 240.9￥/Year',
        href: 'https://www.aliyun.com/minisite/goods?userCode=sna6zh3p',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/alibabacloud.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Zeabur',
        description: 'Serverless Platform | 5$/Month',
        href: 'https://zeabur.com/referral?referralCode=xlinkexe',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/zeabur.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Qiniu',
        description: 'CDN | Free',
        href: 'https://s.qiniu.com/bEnEJn',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/qiniu.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Tencent Cloud',
        description: 'CDN | Overbilling',
        href: 'https://cloud.tencent.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/tencentcloud.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* social-networks */}
  <h2 id='social-networks'>社交网络</h2>
  <p>欢迎关注我的社交网络，与我互动、分享经验、交流知识。</p>
  <Substats
    stats={[
      {
        platform: 'GitHub',
        icon: 'github',
        link: 'https://github.com/ljxme',
        text: 'followers',
        api: 'github/ljxme'
      },
      {
        platform: 'Telegram',
        icon: 'telegram',
        color: '#2ca5e0',
        link: 'https://t.me/ljx_me',
        text: 'members',
        api: 'telegram/ljx_me'
      },
      {
        platform: 'Bilibili',
        icon: 'bilibili',
        color: '#fe7398',
        link: 'https://space.bilibili.com/3546950943115449',
        text: 'fans',
        // api: 'bilibili/3546950943115449'
        count: 1
      },
      {
        platform: 'Steam',
        icon: 'steam',
        color: '#50769d',
        link: 'https://steamcommunity.com/id/ljxme/',
        text: 'games',
        api: 'steamgames/76561199036307152'
      }
    ]}
  />
  <!--
  {/* gossips */}
  <h2 id='gossips'>Gossips</h2>
  <Collapse title='Lorem ipsum'>
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, vidit suscipit at mei. Quem denique mea id. Usu ei regione indoctum
    dissentiunt, cu meliore fuisset mei, vel quod voluptua ne. Ex dicat impedit mel, at eum oratio
    possit voluptatum.
  </Collapse>
  -->
  {/* about-blog */}
  <h2 id='about-blog'>关于博客</h2>
  <p>
    建站碎笔<Spoiler
      >更详细请查看<a href='https://blog.ljx.icu/blog/blog-begin/'>《博客伊始》</a></Spoiler
    >
  </p>
  <Timeline
    events={[
      {
        date: '2025-10-07',
        content:
          '在 <a href="https://wanwang.aliyun.com/" target="_blank">阿里云（原万网）</a> 注册域名 <b>ljx.icu</b> 并选择 <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro</a> 作为框架，<a href="https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure" target="_blank">Astro Theme Pure</a> 作为主题，开始逐渐迁移博客到阿里云服务器。'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-08-26',
        content:
          '在 <a href="https://www.namesilo.com/"target="_blank">NameSilo</a> 注册域名 <b>artemisia.icu</b> ，并用 <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/"target="_blank">Cloudflare</a> 进行域名托管、DNS解析等服务，采用 <a href="https://docs.tangly1024.com/"target="_blank">NotionNext</a> 和 <a href="https://www.notion.com/"target="_blank">Notion</a> 作为博客的框架及内容管理系统。最后博客则静态托管于 <a href="https://vercel.com/"target="_blank">Vercel</a> 。'
      },
      {
        date: '2021-2024',
        content:
          '博客写作换成了 <a href="https://gridea.dev/"target="_blank">Gridea</a> 作为客户端，选择 <a href="https://www.netlify.com/"target="_blank">Netlify</a> 作为托管平台，GitHub仓库只作为源码备份使用。<s>域名都不记得在哪个免费平台薅的了QAQ</s> ，在 <a href="https://digitalplat.org/"target="_blank">DigitalPlat</a> 注册了域名 <b>artemisia.us.kg</b> ，后续因其网站政策原因迁移至 <b>artemisia.dpdns.org</b> ，不过博客也没维护多长时间'
      },
      {
        date: '2019-2020',
        content:
          '初识博客,采用 <a href="https://pages.github.com/"target="_blank">GitHubPages</a> 作为托管平台,开始写作。<s>其实也没怎么写，只是初步接触到了博客这个东西。</s>'
      }
    ]}
  />
  <Collapse title='本网站更新日志'>
    <Timeline
      events={[
        { date: '2026-06-01', content: '更新网站主要字体为 Noto Sans SC' },
        { date: '2025-10-30', content: '更新Waline表情包为自定义表情包' },
        { date: '2025-10-23', content: '完善评论及相关通知类功能，改善签名布局位置' },
        { date: '2025-10-14', content: '实现文章AI摘要功能' },
        { date: '2025-10-13', content: '接入CDN服务，对字体进行分割并使用CDN加速' },
        { date: '2025-10-11', content: '网站所有备案完成' }
      ]}
    />
  </Collapse>
  <p>网站的顺畅运行和个性化定制也依赖于以下优秀项目/服务提供商提供的资源和技术支持：</p>
  <ul>
    <li>域名 & 服务器: <a href='https://www.aliyun.com/' target='_blank'>Aliyun</a></li>
    <li>
      框架 & 主题: <a href='https://astro.build/' target='_blank'>Astro</a> +
      <a href='https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure' target='_blank'>Astro Theme Pure</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      安全保障: <a href='https://www.1panel.cn/' target='_blank'>1Panel</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      国外分流 & CI/CD: <a href='https://www.cloudflare.com/' target='_blank'>Cloudflare</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      CDN: <a href='https://www.dogecloud.com/' target='_blank'>多吉云</a> +
      <a href='https://www.qiniu.com/' target='_blank'>七牛云</a> +
      <a href='https://cloud.tencent.com/' target='_blank'>腾讯云</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      资源加速 & 存储: <a href='https://cdn.jsdmirror.com/' target='_blank'>JSDMirror</a> +
      <a href='https://www.bitiful.com/' target='_blank'>缤纷云</a> +
      <a href='https://imagekit.io/' target='_blank'>Imagekit</a>
    </li>
    <li>评论系统: <a href='https://waline.js.org' target='_blank'>Waline</a></li>
    <li>
      访问统计: <a href='https://supabase.com/' target='_blank'>Supabase</a> +
      <a href='https://waline.js.org/' target='_blank'>Waline</a> +
      <a href='https://www.vercount.one/' target='_blank'>Vercount</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      其他统计: <a href='https://github.com/spencerwooo/substats' target='_blank'>Substats</a>
    </li>
    <li>网站字体: <a href='https://fontsource.org/fonts/noto-sans-sc' target='_blank'>Noto Sans SC</a></li>
  </ul>
  <Collapse title='网站优化结果'>
    <figure class='mt-4'>
      <img
        src='https://tc.ljx.icu/file/imgs/lTEDvghx.png'
        alt='还在优化中🥲'
        loading='lazy'
        class='zoomable rounded shadow max-w-sm md:max-w-md mx-auto my-0'
      />
      <figcaption class='mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 text-center'>
        <a href='/images/youhua.png' target='_blank'>详情图片</a>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <MediumZoom />
  </Collapse>
</PageLayout>
